  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_faction_leaderTitle] of [asker_faction_name], has sent us a message. Apparently, [siteFaction_pawnsPlural] based in a nearby abandoned factory have been raiding their caravans. The factory site is controlled by [siteFaction_name]. It can be a great opportunity to obtain factory elements and mechanoid components.\n\n[asker_nameDef] is asking us to eliminate the threat, and cares not about the fate of the old machine pieces. [asker_label] says that [sitePart0_description].</li>
  -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_faction_leaderTitle] фракции [asker_faction_name], передаёт нам сообщение.\n\nПо всей видимости, [siteFaction_pawnsPlural] из фракции [siteFaction_name] обосновались в производственных зданиях и грабят их караваны. Это отличная возможность получить компоненты механоидов и элементы производства.\n\n[asker_nameDef] желает лишь избавиться от угрозы, а судьба компонентов механоидов [asker_possessive] не волнует. [asker_label] говорит, что [sitePart0_description].</li>
  </VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>


  <!-- EN: Quest expired: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>Время задания истекло: [resolvedQuestName]</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The bandit camp has packed up and moved on. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has expired. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>Механоиды свернули лагерь и отправились в другое место. Время, отведённое для задания [resolvedQuestName], истекло.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest failed: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>Задание провалено: «[resolvedQuestName]»</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: After being discovered, the bandit camp has dispersed. The quest [resolvedQuestName] has ended. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>Поняв, что их местонахождение известно, механоиды свернули лагерь и отправились в другое место. Задание «[resolvedQuestName]» окончено.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextQuestFailed.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Payment arrived -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelPaymentArrived.slateRef>Оплата прибыла</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelPaymentArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: You have defeated the bandit camp!\n\nThe payment from [asker_faction_name] has arrived. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextPaymentArrived.slateRef>Вы уничтожили лагерь механоидов!\n\nПрибыла оплата от фракции [asker_faction_name].</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextPaymentArrived.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelFavorReceiver.slateRef>[asker_faction_royalFavorLabel]</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterLabelFavorReceiver.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: These colonists participated in the victory for the quest [resolvedQuestName]. [asker_definite] wants to know who should receive the [royalFavorReward_amount] [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] for this service. -->
  <VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextFavorReceiver.slateRef>Эти поселенцы приняли участие в успешном завершении задания [resolvedQuestName]. [asker_definite] спрашивает, кому из них за свою службу причитается [royalFavorReward_amount] ед. ^Replace( [asker_faction_royalFavorLabel] | 'милость короны'-'милости короны')^.</VFE_OpportunitySite_AbandonedFactory.LetterTextFavorReceiver.slateRef>
